<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.10.7">
<l>māvali vēḷviyil māṇuru vāycceṉṟu</l>
<l>mūvaṭi tāveṉ ṟirantavim maṇṇiṉai</l>
<l>ōraṭi yiṭṭiraṇ ṭāmaṭi taṉṉilē</l>
<l>tāvaṭi yiṭṭāṉā liṉṟumuṟṟum</l>
<l rend="indent">taraṇi yaḷantāṉā liṉṟumuṟṟum.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having gone to Māvali sacrifice in the form of a dwarf</l>
<l>begging, “give [me] three steps”,</l>
<l rend="indent">he placed one foot [and took] the whole earth</l>
<l rend="indent">[and with] the second foot on that [he took everything];</l>
<l>Because of him who placed his stretched out foot,</l>
<l rend="indent">now we’re at our end</l>
<l>Because of him who measure the earth,</l>
<l rend="indent">now we’re at our end.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
